---
import "@app/styles/global.css";
---

<section
    id="about"
    class="min-h-[70dvh] md:min-h-[80dvh] py-20 md:py-24 container mx-auto flex justify-center items-center"
>
    <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:gap-7 md:gap-8 w-full max-w-8xl text-center"
    >
        <h2
            class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight px-2 sm:px-4 text-zinc-800"
        >
            Nuestra misión, es transformar los retos diarios de tu empresa en
            <span
                class="font-[ibm-plex-serif] font-bold italic text-emerald-900 relative inline-block px-2.5 py-1.5 sm:px-3 sm:py-1.5 md:px-4 md:py-2"
                ><span
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-200/60 -rotate-1 transform origin-center rounded-sm -mx-1"
                ></span><span class="relative z-10"
                    >software, apps y plataformas web</span
                ></span
            >
            que ayuden a operar mejor y crecer con orden.
        </h2>
    </div>
</section>
